359)|Beatrice of Castile]]<ref name=\"EB-Peter I\"/>\n| 26 = 26. Louren\u00e7o Martins<ref name=\"DeSousa1\">{{Cite book |url=https://archive.org/stream/historiagenealog02sous#page/4/mode/2up |title=Historia genealogica da casa real portugueza |trans-title=Genealogical History of the Royal House of Portugal |volume=2 |language=pt |last=de Sousa |first=Antonio Caetano |publisher=Lisboa Occidental |year=1735 |page=4}}</ref>\n| 27 = 27. Sancha Martins<ref name=\"DeSousa1\"/>\n| 28 = 28. [[Edward III of England]]<ref name=\"Armitage-Smith\"/>\n| 29 = 29. [[Philippa of Hainault]]<ref name=\"Armitage-Smith\"/>\n| 30 = 30. [[Henry of Grosmont, 1st Duke of Lancaster]]<ref name=\"Armitage-Smith\"/>\n| 31 = 31. [[Isabel of Beaumont]]<ref name=\"Armitage-Smith\"/>\n}}\n\n{{House of Valois (Burgundy)}}\n\n==Titles==\n* [[File:Blason Charolais.svg|40px]] 1433 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Charolais (county)|Count of Charolais]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Arms of Eudes de Bourgogne.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Duke of Burgundy]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Arms of the Archduchy of Austria.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Dukes of Lothier|Duke of Lothier]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Wapenschild van Brabant.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Dukes of Brabant|Duke of Brabant]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Modern Arms of Limburg.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Dukes of Limburg|Duke of Limburg]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Arms_of_Luxembourg.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Counts, Dukes and Grand Dukes of Luxembourg|Duke of Luxemburg]] as '''Charles II'''\n* [[File:Arms of Flanders.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Counts of Flanders|Count of Flanders]] as '''Charles II'''\n* [[File:Arms of the County of Artois.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Counts of Artois|Count of Artois]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Arms of County of Burgundy.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[List of counts of Burgundy|Count Palatine of Burgundy]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Arms of Flanders.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Counts of Hainaut|Count of Hainault]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Wapen graafschap Holland.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Count of Holland]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:CoA Zeeland Province.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Count of Zeeland]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Wapen van Namen (stad).svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Count of Namur]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Blason be Marquisat d Anvers.svg|40px]] 15 June 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Margrave of Antwerp]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Guelders-J\u00fclich Arms.svg|40px]] 23 February 1473 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Dukes of Guelders|Duke of Guelders]] as '''Charles I'''\n* [[File:Escudo_de_Zutphen_1581.png|40px]] 23 February 1473 \u2013 5 January 1477: [[Count of Zutphen]] as '''Charles I'''\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Biography}}\n* [[Burgundian State]]\n* [[Burgundian Netherlands]]\n* [[Burgundian Wars]]\n* [[Duchy of Burgundy]]\n* [[Dukes of Burgundy family tree]]\n* [[Jacques of Savoy, Count of Romont]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Sources==\n{{Refbegin}}\n* {{EB1911 |last=Poupardin |first=Ren\u00e9 |authorlink=Ren\u00e9 Poupardin |wstitle=Burgundy }}\n* {{EB1911 |last=Poupardin |first=Ren\u00e9 |wstitle=Charles (Duke of Burgundy)|display=Charles, called The Bold, duke of Burgundy}}\n* {{CE1913 |last=Kurth |first=Godefroid |authorlink=Godefroid Kurth |wstitle=Burgundy }}\n<!--* {{Belf|Charles le T\u00e9m\u00e9raire}}-->\n* {{cite book |first=Aline S. |last=Taylor |title=Isabel of Burgundy|url=https://archive.org/details/isabelofburgundy00tayl |url-access=registration }}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{Citation |first=Richard |last=Vaughan |title=Charles the Bold: The Last Valois Duke of Burgundy |location=London |publisher=Longman Group |year=1973 |isbn=0-582-50251-9 }}.\n\n==External links==\n* {{Commons category inline|Charles the Bold}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-hou|[[House of Valois-Burgundy]]|10 November|1433|5 January|1477|[[House of Valois]]}}\n{{S-bef|rows=2|before=[[Philip the Good]]}}\n{{S-ttl|title=[[Duke of Burgundy]], [[Dukes of Brabant|Brabant]],<br>[[Dukes of Limburg|Limburg]], [[Dukes of Lothier|Lothier]] and [[Counts, Dukes and Grand Dukes of Luxembourg|Luxemburg]];<br>[[Marquis of Namur|Margrave of Namur]];<br /> [[Counts of Artois|Count of Artois]], [[Counts of Flanders|Flanders]], <br /> [[Counts of Hainaut|Hainaut]], [[Count of Holland|Holland]] and [[Count of Zeeland|Zeeland]];<br>[[List of counts of Burgundy|Count Palatine of Burgundy]]|years=15 July 1467 \u2013 5 January 1477}}\n{{S-aft|rows=3|after=[[Mary of Burgundy|Mary]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{S-ttl|title=[[Charolais (county)|Count of Charolais]]|years=August 1433 \u2013 5 January 1477}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Arnold, Duke of Gelderland|Arnold]]}}\n{{S-ttl|title=[[Dukes of Guelders|Duke of Guelders]]<br>[[Count of Zutphen]]|years=23 February 1473 \u2013 5 January 1477}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n{{Valois Burgundy}}\n{{Monarchs of Luxembourg}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bold, Charles the}}\n[[Category:Dukes of Burgundy|Charles]]\n[[Category:People of the Burgundian Netherlands]]\n[[Category:House of Valois-Burgundy|Charles]]\n[[Category:1433 births]]\n[[Category:1477 deaths]]\n[[Category:Philip the Good (Duke of Burgundy)|Charles]]\n[[Category:People from Dijon]]\n[[Category:Dukes of Brabant|Charles]]\n[[Category:Dukes of Guelders|Charles]]\n[[Category:Dukes of Limburg|Charles]]\n[[Category:Dukes of Luxembourg|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Flanders|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Artois|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Burgundy|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Hainaut|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Holland|Charles]]\n[[Category:Counts of Charolais|Charles]]\n[[Category:Margraves of Namur|Charles]]\n[[Category:Extra Knights Comp